            '</div>'+
            '<div class="col-md-9">'+
                '<p>“Finding a balance between dishes inspired by authentic recipes and creating a modern take on classic cuisine sees a loyal following of Canberra locals returning for a mouth-watering feast.” – Australian Good Food Guide Website</p>'+
                '<p><a href="http://jewelofindia.com.au/" target="_blank">Click Here</a> for the Jewel of India website.</p>'+
